    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>as I have no frank to <persName ref="pe0157">
                        <sic>M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                            Macgubbin</sic>
                    </persName> I beg leave to inclose this to you &amp; beg
                    you would fill up the direction properly &amp; put it in the post. I am now
                    going out for five weeks &amp; shall be happy to hear from you on my return.</p>
                <closer>
                    <salute>I am D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        <lb/>Sir <lb/>truely y<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>
                    </salute>
                    <signed>
                        <persName ref="pe0232"/>
                    </signed>T Pennant</closer>
                <dateline>
                    <placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> July 27<hi rend="superscript">th.</hi> 1773.</dateline>

                <postscript>
                    <p>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> favor is just come. pray never send anything
                        by <placeName ref="pl0057">Newcastle</placeName> but to <persName ref="pe0026">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> White Bookseller</persName>
                        <placeName ref="pl1012">Fleetstreet London</placeName>. <bibl type="authorial">
                            <title ref="bi0050">Sibbald</title>
                        </bibl> is
                        published: y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Booksellers will get it readier
                        than I can send it: but get one that way &amp; consider it as my gift. &amp;
                        Charge it to me. </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>
                    <address>
                        <addrLine>To</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>M</addrLine>
                    </address>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="superscript">Free</hi>RNBoo<gap reason="illegible" unit="chars" atLeast="3"/>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
